#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=You told me one time about a teacher in school who did something .
#Text=Tell me about that .
#Text=This was in junior-high and I was in special-ed and we would ride the smaller buses .
#Text=So one day my bus was late and we were there , a group of kids , we were waiting for the bus .
#Text=By this time some of the teachers were leaving .
#Text=And there was one particular teacher that was leaving , and as he passed by he told me , " Wow , where did you get that thing from ? "
#Text=And I was shocked .
#Text=He said , " Oh , never mind , I thought you were wearing a mask . "
#Text=It really hurt me because it was embarrassing and I had some friends with me — and it was a teacher .
#Text=And I just felt really let down and betrayed because a teacher said this .
#Text=And after he realized his mistake he never apologized , and that really hurt me .
#Text=Have you encountered other incidents like this ?
#Text=There were a few .
#Text=One that really springs to mind , was when I was going to an electronics store .
#Text=My mom and I were walking to the door .
#Text=We saw one of the managers locked the door and wave us away .
#Text=I knew they were n't closed , it was in the middle of the afternoon on a Saturday , and there were people walking around , shopping .
#Text=And he just locked the door and waved me away .
#Text=What about others in your family with NF ?
#Text=Well , I 'm the youngest of six , I have two sisters that have NF and they have milder cases .
#Text=They have a few tumors on their body but none that are really disfiguring .
#Text=And also , I had a brother , one other brother , that had neurofibromatosis .
#Text=He had some of the tumors .
#Text=He also developed a neurosarcoma , he was about 46-years old and one of his tumors turned to cancer .
#Text=That was really difficult for all of us because it was unexpected .
#Text=My mom , she has it and she also has a few of the small tumors .
#Text=Other than that , there is no one else in the family that have it .
#Text=A head to toe body tour
#Text=If we had a tour of your body , show me from the head to your arms to your leg , how NF has affected you .
#Text=NF has affected me by some of the tumors on my arms , and , I have a few on my back ...
#Text=Can you show me your arm ?
#Text=My arms ?
#Text=Like here , some of the tumors right here ...
#Text=Okay , you point to , like , the one on your elbow .
#Text=Does that hurt ?
#Text=No this is very soft , and it does n't hurt .
#Text=And there 's one here , and one here , and there 's a few here ...
